<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Doctor Confirmation Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #d9534f;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
      background-color: #28a745;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .content, .header, .footer {
        padding: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Doctor Confirmation Reminder</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear Admin,</p>
      <p>The following appointment is scheduled to start in <span class="highlight">{{sTime}} - {{eTime}}</span> and is <strong>Approved</strong>, but the doctor has not yet confirmed it:</p>
      
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Doctor:</strong>{{doctor}}</li>
        <li><strong>Patient:</strong>{{customer}}</li>
        <li><strong>Appointment Time:</strong>{{date}} {{time}}</li>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> Approved (Doctor <span class="highlight">Not Confirmed</span>)</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Please follow up with the doctor to ensure they are prepared for the appointment.</p>

      <a href="{{appURL}}" class="button">View Appointment Details</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>From,</p>
      <p>Administration Team,</p>
      <p>Mobilab2u.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
